  Line 1: FULL NAME
  Line 2: professional headline / target title
  Line 3: compact contact line

Photo block rules:

  Placement: top-right
  Shape: rectangle
  Width target: 32 mm
  Height: proportional to source image
  Alignment: top-aligned with name block region
  No shadow
  No thick border
  Optional hairline border only if needed

