TWO-PAGE EXTENSION LOGIC IF CONTENT REQUIRES IT:

If the CV flows to page 2, maintain this structure:

Page 1:

* Header with photo
* Summary
* Competencies
* Most recent and most important experience entries

Page 2:

* Remaining experience
* Education
* Certifications
* Languages
* Technical skills
* Additional information if still relevant

